XKService Todo List
===================

High Priority Tasks
-------------------
 - Use the table tblGPRS table to determine if there are new
   alerts from the start instead of scanning devices.

Medium Priority Tasks
---------------------
 - Implement advanced logging settings (debug, custom log file,
   or syslog) in the configuration.
 - Create configuration files for the service configuration.
   Include settings for alert checking, cleanups, and database
   configurations.
 - Implement an SMTP client using Boost possibly instead of
   using the mail command.
